title: The Mysterious Pilot (1937) Old Time Serial (OTS)
description:
From 1937 comes 15 somewhat boring episodes of The Mysterious Pilot in glorious Black and White.  Canoes chases and plane crashes. 10 crashes in 15 episodes.  I expect there were lots of models used.  They could not afford to lose 10 real airplanes even if they were made of wood and canvas!

Plot: A pilot and mapmaker for the Royal Canadian Air Force shields a woman from the villainous machinations of her former fiance
